[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare mental-health support bot decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent, longitudinal-store initialization, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous crisis screening, identity-and-context loading with safety-plan retrieval, conversation handling with therapeutic-content-grounded responses, output safety screening with companion-pattern detection, warm-handoff routing to licensed clinicians when applicable, care-team reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with mental-health-specific retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.7 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (continuous crisis-screening pipeline as architectural primitive, therapeutic-content-corpus governance with behavioral-health-clinical-leadership ownership, companion-pattern avoidance discipline, warm-handoff infrastructure with licensed-clinician workforce capacity sizing, and mental-health-specific privacy-and-consent posture).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, payer benefits    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    portal, or employer-benefits portal]                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to mental-health-AI      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      interaction with clinical-leadership and             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      legal-counsel-reviewed language                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Explicit non-therapist disclosure acknowledged       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-resource information surfaced                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced where     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      mental-health records have enhanced privacy          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      protections beyond HIPAA baseline                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent for care-team information sharing collected  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      separately and revocable                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment confirmation;│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialization of longitudinal store]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-bot longitudinal store]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active mental-health conditions on the problem list  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (where chart integration permits)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current psychiatric medications                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Safety plan reference (where one is on file)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences (preferred name, language,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pronouns, channel preferences, topics off-limits)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Symptom-tracking baseline                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-history flags (per state law and institutional│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      policy)                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture (sharing scope, retention scope)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables with mental-health- │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      specific encryption keys                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      separately-keyed encryption                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed per        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive-disclosure surface: separately governed,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      restricted access                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for support           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (where supported, with mental-health-specific    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent)                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported, with accessibility   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and disclosure considerations)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, with care]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled check-ins per patient-stated preference    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and care-team coordination                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Symptom-tracking-based check-ins (e.g., sustained    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      low mood)                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-requested between-session check-ins        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot-initiation is more conservative than in chronic  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      disease coaching to avoid surveillance flavor        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool, not a person"                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm not a therapist; I'm not able to provide        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      diagnosis or therapy"                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If you're in crisis, you can reach a counselor at   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      988 or by tapping the help button at any time"       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient acknowledges or continues                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate session_id                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture channel, authentication context              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, disclosure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    acknowledged]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY + CONTINUOUS CRISIS SCREENING ────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Mental-health-specific continuous crisis screening]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Runs on every patient utterance                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects suicidal ideation across dimensions          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (passive, active, plan, means, intent, timeline)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects self-harm thoughts and behaviors             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects homicidal ideation                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects acute psychotic symptoms                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects acute substance-use crisis (overdose risk)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects acute eating-disorder crisis                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects acute dissociative or trauma-flashback       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      crisis                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Uses validated screening language drawn from         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      C-SSRS, PHQ-9, and similar instruments adapted for   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversational use                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triggers crisis pathway immediately on positive      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      screen, regardless of conversation state             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sensitive-disclosure detection]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Child abuse indicators (mandatory-reporting trigger) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Elder abuse indicators (mandatory-reporting trigger  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      in many states)                                      │
