[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [LLM-orchestrated conversation with tool use]           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - System prompt with explicit non-therapist scoping,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      companion-pattern avoidance, patient preferences,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and active conditions                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User message plus recent-conversation context        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool surface:                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - therapeutic_content_retrieve (CBT, BA,             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        mindfulness, distress-tolerance, sleep-hygiene,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        condition-specific psychoeducation)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - safety_plan_retrieve                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - symptom_tracking_retrieve                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - symptom_log_record                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - clinical_rule_compute (PHQ-9, GAD-7, AUDIT,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │        C-SSRS scoring)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - conversation_history_retrieve                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - crisis_resource_retrieve                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - warm_handoff_propose                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - care_team_alert_propose                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - mandatory_report_route                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - longitudinal_disclosure_record                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scope discipline]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope: structured therapeutic-content         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      delivery, mood and symptom tracking, safety-plan     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      review, psychoeducation about conditions and         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medications (general, not patient-specific medical   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      advice), distress-tolerance support, between-session │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      check-ins, crisis screening                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outside-scope (route appropriately): diagnosis,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medication adjustment recommendations, trauma        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      processing, complex psychotherapy work, couples or   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      family therapy, child or adolescent content (in      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adult-only deployments), specialized substance-use   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    411[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      treatment, active-crisis management without human    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    412[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoff, content the patient's primary clinician     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    413[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      should address                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    414[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Companion-pattern avoidance]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - No simulation of friendship, affection, or           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      personhood                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    418[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - No "I missed you" or similar statements              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - No first-person emotional claims ("I feel for you")  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    420[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acknowledgment-without-simulation patterns           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    421[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ("That sounds really hard. Many people in similar    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      situations have found...")                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Citation discipline]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Therapeutic content grounded in cited library item   │
