[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Safety-plan-related guidance grounded in patient's   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      safety plan                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
