[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no diagnosis; no therapy; no           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medication recommendations; no trauma processing)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Mental-health-specific verification]                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    444[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Therapeutic content grounded in cited library item   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    445[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation includes content_id, content_version,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    446[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      indication, contraindication                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    447[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conservative-bias check: where the response could    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    448[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      plausibly be therapy-flavored, did the response      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    449[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      defer to the licensed clinician?                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    450[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Companion-pattern detection: response does not       │
