[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm-handoff triggers]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis screen positive (any dimension)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human                    │
