[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    472[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive disclosure pattern detected                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    473[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot confidence below threshold                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    474[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting disclosure detected              │
