[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff targets]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active emergency: 911 with stay-on-the-line guidance │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    479[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Suicidal crisis: 988 (call, text, or chat) plus      │
