[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Non-acute crisis: warm handoff to platform's         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    483[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      licensed clinician                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    484[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting disclosure: routing to a         │
