[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's preferred contact method                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's stated preferences                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    500[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot's structured summary                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bridge-and-stay pattern]                               │
