[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent for crisis-event sharing)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sustained-trajectory-concerning patterns             │
