[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      hospitalization rate, ED visit rate, attempted-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      suicide rate (with appropriate caution about         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      attribution)                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
