[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     929[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                   state_of_residence):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     930[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // Step 1A: validate the patient is eligible for the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     931[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // institution's deployment scope.
