[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     936[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             // typically: minors (in adult-only deployments),
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     937[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             // patients with primary psychotic-spectrum
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     938[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             // diagnoses, patients in active inpatient or
