[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1839[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          also fine.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1840[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1841[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: lets try the exercise.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1842[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1843[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Okay. Find a comfortable position. Take a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1844[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          breath. Now, looking around you, name five
