[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1855[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1856[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: blanket weight. pillow. cool side of the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1857[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          pillow. my phone in my hand.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1858[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1859[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Three things you can hear.
