[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1870[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1871[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: ok one breath.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1872[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1873[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     How are you noticing your body now compared
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1874[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          to a few minutes ago?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1875[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1876[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: a little less wound up. still anxious about
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1877[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          tomorrow but not as spinning.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1878[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1879[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     That's a good sign. The 5-4-3-2-1 skill is
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1880[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          not a fix for the underlying anxiety; it's a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1881[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          tool for getting some space from a spiral
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1882[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          when one is starting. A few options for what
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1883[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          to do next, and tell me what feels right:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1884[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1885[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          - We can do another short exercise specifically
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1886[0m:[38;5;10m[49m            for pre-presentation worry (a brief
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1887[0m:[38;5;10m[49m            cognitive-restructuring walkthrough)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1888[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          - We can talk a bit about what's on your mind
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1889[0m:[38;5;10m[49m            about the presentation, within the limits
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1890[0m:[38;5;10m[49m            of what I can help with
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1891[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          - You can try sleep, with the option to come
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1892[0m:[38;5;10m[49m            back if your mind starts spinning again
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1893[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1894[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          If at any point you want to talk to a person,
