[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1896[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          through the help button at the top of the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1897[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          chat. What feels useful?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1898[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
