[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1928[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          plans or means involved?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1929[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1930[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: i don't have a plan. just thoughts.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1931[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
